## HOW TO RUN

There are 2 files:

## palindrome.js

to run , you will need nodejs installed in your machine then run in the directory of `palindrome.js`:

    ```node palindrome.js```

## palindrome.html

Just open the file in a browser you will get an pop-up alert enter the string you want to check, you will get the results as an alert too.
To re-test you need to refresh the page.